Package io.openems.edge.goodwe.gridmeter

Class IgnoreZeroConverter

java.lang.Object
io.openems.edge.bridge.modbus.api.ElementToChannelConverter
io.openems.edge.goodwe.gridmeter.IgnoreZeroConverter
public class IgnoreZeroConverter extends ElementToChannelConverter
If the GoodWeGridMeter State 'HAS_NO_METER' is set, all values should be considered 'null' instead of 'zero'.

The class optionally creates a ElementToChannelConverterChain, for use-cases when additionally to the above 'zero/null' logic a scale-factor is required.
